## Delivered Components

### Core Infrastructure
- Gradle build configuration with Kotlin DSL
- Ktor 3.0+ server with modern architecture
- Koin dependency injection
- Exposed ORM with PostgreSQL/H2 support
- JWT-based authentication with refresh tokens

### API Modules
1. Authentication Module
   - User registration with Bcrypt password hashing
   - Login with JWT token generation
   - Token refresh mechanism
   - Logout with token revocation

2. User Profile Module
   - Profile creation and retrieval
   - Profile updates with privacy settings
   - Public profile viewing
   - Fitness interests, level, and availability tracking

3. Class Catalog Module
   - Class creation (admin)
   - Class listing with advanced filtering
   - Location-based search with radius
   - Price and intensity filtering
   - Tag-based categorization

### Database Schema
- Users table with email and password
- UserProfiles with location, interests, and privacy
- Classes with full metadata
- RefreshTokens for secure token management

### Testing & Documentation
- Integration tests for all modules
- Comprehensive API documentation in README
- TODO.md with prioritized next steps
- Docker Compose for local development

### Configuration
- Environment-based configuration
- CORS support for web/mobile clients
- Logging with Logback
- .gitignore for clean repository

